                                    hospitality industry, this special class of software is ideally suited
                                    for use at hotels, military guest houses, motels, resorts, inns, lodges,
                                    hostel, suites, ranch, apartments, medical centers and bed and breakfast
                                    operations. A few of the important modules that come built-in the PM
                                    Software are: <b>Hotel Management Software</b>, Hotel Reservation
                                    Software (Billing Software), Hotel PMS, Hotel Reception Software and Hotel
                                    accounting software. All the modules and programs in this lodging
                                    software are closely incorporated and come at no additional cost.<br />
